Mission & Culture
Mission
We exist to entertain and captivate people through impactful and engaging mobile applications.
We want to spark strong positive emotions in everyone who uses our products.
Our values
At Tipsy Flamingo, we all share 4 values.
Creativity
We’re all hackers and we’re always chasing novelty: it’s the only way to create something big.
Simplicity
We think that beauty is self-evident.
Obsessed with Perfection
We are always looking for the most elegant, simple and beautiful ways to solve problems.
Think big
We push ourselves to work on disruptive, unique and impactful ideas.